igmp.name: igmp

revisions.description: Initial version, to support IGMP membership status polling.

igmp.contactinfo: Stan Xiang,Hamish Kellahan Allied Telesis EMail: support@alliedtelesis.co.nz
igmp.description: The MIB module for IGMP Management.

igmpInterfaceTable.name: igmpInterfaceTable
igmpInterfaceTable.description: The (conceptual) table listing IGMP capable IP interfaces.

igmpInterfaceEntry.name: igmpInterfaceEntry
igmpInterfaceEntry.description: An entry (conceptual row) in the igmpInterfaceTable.

igmpInterface.name: igmpInterface
igmpInterface.description: The index value of the interface for which IGMP is enabled. This table is indexed by this value.

igmpInterfaceName.name: igmpInterfaceName
igmpInterfaceName.description: The name of the interface for which IGMP or MLD is enabled.

igmpQueryTimeout.name: igmpQueryTimeout
igmpQueryTimeout.description: It represents the maximum expected time interval, in seconds, between successive IGMP general query messages arriving on the interface. A vlaue of zero means there is no limits.

igmpProxy.name: igmpProxy
igmpProxy.description: The object represents states of igmp proxy. When it has a value of 0 then it means the inteface proxy is currently disabled. When it has a value of 1 then it means IGMP is performing upstream inteface proxying. When it has a value of 2 then it means IGMP is performing downstream inteface proxying.

igmpIntStatsTable.name: igmpIntStatsTable
igmpIntStatsTable.description: The (conceptual) table listing statistics for IGMP capable IP interfaces.

igmpIntStatsEntry.name: igmpIntStatsEntry
igmpIntStatsEntry.description: An entry (conceptual row) in the igmpIntStatsTable.

igmpInQuery.name: igmpInQuery
igmpInQuery.description: The number of IGMP Query messages received by the interface.

igmpInReportV1.name: igmpInReportV1
igmpInReportV1.description: The number of IGMP version 1 Report messages received by the interface.

igmpInReportV2.name: igmpInReportV2
igmpInReportV2.description: The number of IGMP version 2 Report messages received by the interface.

igmpInLeave.name: igmpInLeave
igmpInLeave.description: The number of IGMP Leave Group messages received by the interface.

igmpInTotal.name: igmpInTotal
igmpInTotal.description: The total number of IGMP messages received by the interface.

igmpOutQuery.name: igmpOutQuery
igmpOutQuery.description: The total number of IGMP Query messages that were transmitted by the switch over the interface.

igmpOutTotal.name: igmpOutTotal
igmpOutTotal.description: The total number of IGMP messages that were transmitted by the switch over the interface.

igmpBadQuery.name: igmpBadQuery
igmpBadQuery.description: The number of IGMP membership query messages with errors that were received by the interface.

igmpBadReportV1.name: igmpBadReportV1
igmpBadReportV1.description: The number of IGMP Version 1 membership report messages with errors that were received by the interface.

igmpBadReportV2.name: igmpBadReportV2
igmpBadReportV2.description: The number of IGMP Version 2 membership report messages with errors that were received by the interface.

igmpBadLeave.name: igmpBadLeave
igmpBadLeave.description: The number of IGMP Leave Group messages with errors that were received by the interface.

igmpBadTotal.name: igmpBadTotal
igmpBadTotal.description: The total number of IGMP messages with errors that were received by the interface..

igmpIntGroupTable.name: igmpIntGroupTable
igmpIntGroupTable.description: The (conceptual) table listing the IP multicast groups of which there are members on a particular interface.

igmpIntGroupEntry.name: igmpIntGroupEntry
igmpIntGroupEntry.description: An entry (conceptual row) in the igmpGroupTable.

igmpIntGroupAddress.name: igmpIntGroupAddress
igmpIntGroupAddress.description: The IP multicast group address for which this entry contains information.

igmpLastHost.name: igmpLastHost
igmpLastHost.description: The IP address of the last host reporting a membership. If it is static, then 0.0.0.0 presents.

igmpRefreshTime.name: igmpRefreshTime
igmpRefreshTime.description: The time in seconds until the membership group is deleted if another membership report is not received. A value of 0xffffffff means infinity.

igmpSnoopAdminEnabled.name: igmpSnoopAdminEnabled
igmpSnoopAdminEnabled.description: Indicates whether IGMP Snooping is globally enabled.

igmpSnoopVlanTable.name: igmpSnoopVlanTable
igmpSnoopVlanTable.description: The (conceptual) table listing the layer 2 interfaces performing IGMP snooping.

igmpSnoopVlanEntry.name: igmpSnoopVlanEntry
igmpSnoopVlanEntry.description: An entry (conceptual row) in the IGMP Snooping Vlan Table.

igmpSnoopVID.name: igmpSnoopVID
igmpSnoopVID.description: The 802.1 VLAN ID of the layer 2 interface performing IGMP snooping.

igmpSnoopVlanName.name: igmpSnoopVlanName
igmpSnoopVlanName.description: The name of the layer 2 interface performing IGMP snooping.

igmpSnoopFastLeave.name: igmpSnoopFastLeave
igmpSnoopFastLeave.description: Indicates whether FastLeave is enabled, and operating in Single-Host or Multi-Host mode.

igmpSnoopQuerySolicit.name: igmpSnoopQuerySolicit
igmpSnoopQuerySolicit.description: Indicates whether query solicitation is on

igmpSnoopStaticRouterPorts.name: igmpSnoopStaticRouterPorts
igmpSnoopStaticRouterPorts.description: Indicates the configured static multicast router ports.

igmpSnoopGroupTable.name: igmpSnoopGroupTable
igmpSnoopGroupTable.description: The (conceptual) table of IGMP Groups snooped on a layer 2 interface.

igmpSnoopGroupEntry.name: igmpSnoopGroupEntry
igmpSnoopGroupEntry.description: A (conceptual) row in the IGMP Snooping Group table.

igmpSnoopGroupAddress.name: igmpSnoopGroupAddress
igmpSnoopGroupAddress.description: The Multicast Group IP Address detected on a layer 2 interface.

igmpSnoopGroupTimer.name: igmpSnoopGroupTimer
igmpSnoopGroupTimer.description: The time remaining before the multicast group is deleted from the layer 2 interface.

igmpSnoopPortTable.name: igmpSnoopPortTable
igmpSnoopPortTable.description: A (conceptual) table of ports in a layer 2 interface that are currently members of a multicast group.

igmpSnoopPortEntry.name: igmpSnoopPortEntry
igmpSnoopPortEntry.description: A (conceptual) row in the IGMP Snooping Port Table.

igmpSnoopPortNumber.name: igmpSnoopPortNumber
igmpSnoopPortNumber.description: Provides the number of a port in a multicast group.

igmpSnoopPortIsStatic.name: igmpSnoopPortIsStatic
igmpSnoopPortIsStatic.description: Indicates whether a port has been administratively added to a multicast group.

igmpSnoopPortTimer.name: igmpSnoopPortTimer
igmpSnoopPortTimer.description: Indicates the time remaining before the port is removed.

igmpSnoopHostTable.name: igmpSnoopHostTable
igmpSnoopHostTable.description: A (conceptual) table of hosts receiving multicast data.

igmpSnoopHostEntry.name: igmpSnoopHostEntry
igmpSnoopHostEntry.description: A (conceptual) row in the IGMP Snooping Host Table.

igmpSnoopHostMAC.name: igmpSnoopHostMAC
igmpSnoopHostMAC.description: Provides the Media Access Control Address of an IGMP Host.

igmpSnoopHostIpAddress.name: igmpSnoopHostIpAddress
igmpSnoopHostIpAddress.description: Provides the Internet Protocol Address of an IGMP Host.

igmpSnoopHostTimer.name: igmpSnoopHostTimer
igmpSnoopHostTimer.description: Indicates the time remaining before the host times out.
